  title `Repeal of Act 14 of 1935.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_49_content
  footnotes `1. Subs. by Act 4 of 1947, s. 4, for s. 49.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_11_12_00012_194207_1523353762094&sectionId=47648&sectionno=49&orderno=57&orgactid=AC_CEN_11_12_00012_194207_1523353762094
obj_root_law_sections_49_content:
  string
  line `^1[49. Repeal of Act 14 of 1935.--The Indian Coffee Cess Act, 1935 (14 of 1935), is hereby`
  line repealed.]
